<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UniConnect | One Platform. Endless Opportunities.</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* --- CSS STYLES --- */
        :root {
            --primary-blue: #2563eb;
            --primary-green: #22c55e;
            --text-dark: #1f2937;
            --text-gray: #6b7280;
            --bg-light: #f9fafb;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 6%;
            background: #fff;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 40px;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav ul li a.active, nav ul li a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-green);
        }

        .nav-right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .search-bar {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .search-bar input {
            padding: 0.6rem 1rem 0.6rem 2.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 50px;
            width: 250px;
            background: #f3f4f6;
        }

        .search-bar i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-gray);
        }

        .btn-login {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .btn-signup {
            background: var(--primary-blue);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 4rem 6%;
            gap: 4rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #f0fdf4);
        }

        .hero-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .badge-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: var(--primary-green);
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .badge-tag span {
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .hero-content h1 span.blue { color: var(--primary-blue); }
        .hero-content h1 span.green { color: var(--primary-green); }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .hero-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .btn-get-started {
            background: var(--primary-blue);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .btn-explore {
            background: white;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .social-proof {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .student-avatars {
            display: flex;
        }

        .student-avatars img {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid white;
            margin-left: -12px;
        }

        .student-avatars img:first-child { margin-left: 0; }

        .social-proof p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .hero-image {
            flex: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-image img.main-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Feature Section */
        .features {
            padding: 5rem 6%;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .features h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .features > p {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
            text-align: left;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .icon-box {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .blue-icon { background: #eff6ff; color: #3b82f6; }
        .green-icon { background: #f0fdf4; color: #22c55e; }
        .orange-icon { background: #fffbeb; color: #f59e0b; }
        .purple-icon { background: #f5f3ff; color: #8b5cf6; }
        .pink-icon { background: #fff1f2; color: #ec4899; }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Profile image in nav bar update */
        .nav-user-img {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="images/UClogo.png" alt="UniConnect Logo">
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Events</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Features</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="nav-right">
            <div class="search-bar">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Search events, workshops, seminars...">
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="btn-login">Login</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn-signup">Sign Up</a>
            <img src="images/100.jpg" alt="Profile" class="nav-user-img">
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="badge-tag">
                <span>●</span> Your Campus, Your Connection
            </div>
            <h1>One Platform.<br>Endless <span class="green">Opportunities.</span></h1>
            <p>Join events, manage your schedule, volunteer and connect with your campus community.</p>
            
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a href="#" class="btn-get-started">Get Started &rarr;</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn-explore">Explore Events <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i></a>
            </div>

            <div class="social-proof">
                <div class="student-avatars">
                    <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=1" alt="Student">
                    <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=2" alt="Student">
                    <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=3" alt="Student">
                    <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=4" alt="Student">
                </div>
                <p>Join <span style="color: var(--primary-blue); font-weight: bold;">5,000+</span> students already connected</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="ChatGPT Image Apr 26, 2026, 11_43_49 AM.jpg" alt="Students with laptop" class="main-img">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <h2>Everything you need in one place</h2>
        <p>Powerful features to simplify your campus life</p>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-box blue-icon">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Discover Events</h3>
                <p>Find events, workshops, seminars and activities happening on campus.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-box green-icon">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-day"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Smart Schedule</h3>
                <p>Organize your time and never miss an important event.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-box orange-icon">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-address-card"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Easy Registration</h3>
                <p>Register for events in just a few clicks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-box purple-icon">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-bell"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Stay Updated</h3>
                <p>Get notifications and updates about events you care about.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-box pink-icon">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Get Involved</h3>
                <p>Volunteer, participate and make a difference on campus.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>